---
title: Swiss Chard & Wild Mushroom Penne with Chili and Parmesan
description: Garlicky wild mushrooms and Swiss chard are front and center in this creamy pasta. We've spiced it up with a touch of paprika and a dash of chili flakes. A sprinkling of Parmesan finishes the dish off right.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/568d73d3fd2cb9a50f8b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/568d73d3fd2cb9a50f8b4567.pdf
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
course: main course
